Package: precision-7780-audio-fix
Version: 1.0.0-1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Installed-Size: 4
Maintainer: tkirkland <tony@tonykirkland.net>
Depends: initramfs-tools, alsa-utils, pipewire-audio, pipewire-pulse, wireplumber, firmware-sof-signed, firmware-intel-sound
Recommends: libspa-0.2-bluetooth, pulseaudio-utils, pavucontrol
Description: Audio configuration for the Dell Precision 7780
 Forces the Intel SOF driver for the Precision 7780 SoundWire audio interface
 and digital microphone array. The package also pulls in the Debian PipeWire,
 WirePlumber, ALSA, and Intel SOF firmware packages required by the system.
